text: Zoran Milinković (Зоран Милинковић; born 26 September 1956) was the presidential candidate of the Patriots of the Serbian Diaspora in the 2004 Serbian presidential election.http://www.b92.net/specijal/izbori2004/vesti.php?start=330& He was born in Kraljevo, but from 1980th lives in Paris and he led anti-NATO demonstrations in France. He is the owner of Yu Business World review. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kraljevo Category:Candidates for President of Serbia
title: Zoran Milinković (politician)
